-- North Korea Proposes UN Talks Tomorrow on Ship Sinking, Yonhap Reports
-- Seonjin Cha
-- 2010-07-13T22:15:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-13/north-korea-proposes-un-talks-tomorrow-on-ship-sinking-yonhap-reports.html

          
          
             North Korea proposed talks with 
officials from the United Nations Command tomorrow after it
canceled a planned meeting yesterday, Yonhap News reported,  
citing unidentified South Korean military officials.  
 North Korea and the UN Command have planned the meeting to
discuss the sinking of a South Korean warship in March.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
